00:23:56.590 --> 00:24:00.430 align:middle line:84%
So isn't now the planet
ready to defend itself

00:24:00.430 --> 00:24:01.790 align:middle line:90%
against the Draco?

00:24:01.790 --> 00:24:04.240 align:middle line:84%
>>RICE: There is a certain
irony in there, isn't there?

00:24:04.240 --> 00:24:05.380 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Yeah.

00:24:05.380 --> 00:24:07.090 align:middle line:84%
>>RICE: The Draco's
plan, keep in mind,

00:24:07.090 --> 00:24:10.960 align:middle line:84%
is the bonding and
melding of being

00:24:10.960 --> 00:24:16.460 align:middle line:84%
with technology, what Earth
refers to as transhumanism.

00:24:16.460 --> 00:24:18.680 align:middle line:84%
And once they are
able to replace

00:24:18.680 --> 00:24:21.890 align:middle line:84%
a large portion of the
biological processes

00:24:21.890 --> 00:24:25.250 align:middle line:84%
with technology, that
is their ultimate goal

00:24:25.250 --> 00:24:27.470 align:middle line:84%
because then they
can individually

00:24:27.470 --> 00:24:33.050 align:middle line:84%
control in the fullest extent
every single being that's

00:24:33.050 --> 00:24:34.410 align:middle line:90%
on the planet.

00:24:34.410 --> 00:24:37.310 align:middle line:84%
So it doesn't
matter if they think

00:24:37.310 --> 00:24:40.340 align:middle line:84%
they have the ability to
defend themselves and stand up

00:24:40.340 --> 00:24:41.600 align:middle line:90%
to the Draco.

00:24:41.600 --> 00:24:46.130 align:middle line:84%
If they remain on that path
of becoming mostly machine

00:24:46.130 --> 00:24:50.180 align:middle line:84%
and partly live
being, then they are

00:24:50.180 --> 00:24:53.690 align:middle line:84%
handing over their free
will and relinquishing it

00:24:53.690 --> 00:24:55.190 align:middle line:90%
to being controlled.

00:24:55.190 --> 00:24:56.690 align:middle line:84%
And it doesn't
matter whether or not

00:24:56.690 --> 00:25:02.030 align:middle line:84%
they've got all the tanks or ion
cannons or defensive structures

00:25:02.030 --> 00:25:06.110 align:middle line:84%
because each and every person
within have that control

00:25:06.110 --> 00:25:09.470 align:middle line:84%
mechanism in place where they
don't have the free will.

00:25:09.470 --> 00:25:14.090 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: So if you have 13
families running a society,

00:25:14.090 --> 00:25:18.870 align:middle line:84%
you're going to get a stratified
society, a class system,

00:25:18.870 --> 00:25:19.670 align:middle line:90%
all right?

00:25:19.670 --> 00:25:22.290 align:middle line:84%
They didn't really have a
class system before the war.

00:25:22.290 --> 00:25:23.090 align:middle line:90%
>>RICE: Correct.

00:25:23.090 --> 00:25:24.740 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: But now they're
going to have one.

00:25:24.740 --> 00:25:25.540 align:middle line:90%
>>RICE: Mm-hmm.

00:25:25.540 --> 00:25:29.420 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: How do the
population react to the idea

00:25:29.420 --> 00:25:31.730 align:middle line:84%
that they are now entering
into a class system

00:25:31.730 --> 00:25:35.270 align:middle line:84%
and some people are going to
be more elite than others,

00:25:35.270 --> 00:25:39.595 align:middle line:84%
have more riches, have
more freedoms than others?

00:25:39.595 --> 00:25:41.660 align:middle line:84%
There must have been
some resentment.

00:25:41.660 --> 00:25:45.350 align:middle line:84%
>>RICE: The resentment was
expressed through the very

00:25:45.350 --> 00:25:47.140 align:middle line:90%
short-lived rebellion.

00:25:47.140 --> 00:25:50.480 align:middle line:84%
The rest of the
population were either

00:25:50.480 --> 00:25:54.980 align:middle line:84%
too shellshocked to
realize it, or they

00:25:54.980 --> 00:25:59.870 align:middle line:84%
had consented because they
were no longer in fear of being

00:25:59.870 --> 00:26:02.060 align:middle line:90%
killed by an invading army.

00:26:02.060 --> 00:26:08.150 align:middle line:84%
And so by relinquishing those
rights in exchange for safety,

00:26:08.150 --> 00:26:10.748 align:middle line:90%
they had accepted that.

00:26:10.748 --> 00:26:12.290 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: They had
accepted that they're

00:26:12.290 --> 00:26:14.253 align:middle line:84%
going to be ruled
by these 13 families

00:26:14.253 --> 00:26:15.920 align:middle line:84%
that they didn't even
know about before.

00:26:15.920 --> 00:26:17.410 align:middle line:90%
>>RICE: Correct.

00:26:17.410 --> 00:26:20.200 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: Well that's
quite a trick.

00:26:20.200 --> 00:26:23.440 align:middle line:84%
>>RICE: Keep them busy, keep
them distracted, and keep them

00:26:23.440 --> 00:26:24.880 align:middle line:90%
occupied elsewhere.

00:26:24.880 --> 00:26:26.380 align:middle line:84%
And then before you
know it, there's

00:26:26.380 --> 00:26:28.690 align:middle line:84%
an entire system in place
that's controlling them

00:26:28.690 --> 00:26:30.740 align:middle line:84%
that had been
around for decades.

00:26:30.740 --> 00:26:33.760 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: Do they have
media on this planet?

00:26:33.760 --> 00:26:34.820 align:middle line:90%
>>RICE: No, they did not.

00:26:34.820 --> 00:26:35.620 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: No media.

00:26:35.620 --> 00:26:39.480 align:middle line:84%
No newspapers, no radios,
no television, no magazines,

00:26:39.480 --> 00:26:40.360 align:middle line:90%
no books?

00:26:40.360 --> 00:26:41.160 align:middle line:90%
>>RICE: Nope.

00:26:41.160 --> 00:26:44.320 align:middle line:84%
Just educational material
that was needed for training.

00:26:44.320 --> 00:26:49.450 align:middle line:84%
Because again, you got to think
during this transition period,

00:26:49.450 --> 00:26:54.490 align:middle line:84%
people were working for extended
periods of time contributing.

00:26:54.490 --> 00:27:01.930 align:middle line:84%
And there was an amazing amount
of co-creative contribution

00:27:01.930 --> 00:27:05.350 align:middle line:84%
to rebuilding the
planet, and everybody

00:27:05.350 --> 00:27:07.310 align:middle line:90%
was interested in helping.

00:27:07.310 --> 00:27:13.850 align:middle line:84%
And so hiding it behind
let's rebuild our planet,

00:27:13.850 --> 00:27:18.140 align:middle line:84%
people weren't focused on
what are the politics going on

00:27:18.140 --> 00:27:20.940 align:middle line:84%
behind the scenes that we're
relinquishing our control,

00:27:20.940 --> 00:27:23.510 align:middle line:84%
and there is now
a divided society

00:27:23.510 --> 00:27:25.730 align:middle line:90%
which we have two classes.

00:27:25.730 --> 00:27:27.370 align:middle line:84%
People weren't
thinking about that.

00:27:27.370 --> 00:27:30.860 align:middle line:84%
They were occupied with
the rebuilding efforts.

00:27:30.860 --> 00:27:33.710 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: Usually after a really
big war where a lot of people

00:27:33.710 --> 00:27:37.310 align:middle line:84%
are lost, there
is a big huge boom

00:27:37.310 --> 00:27:41.270 align:middle line:84%
of children following that,
