that were operated by Earth
corporations, four Earth

00:30:38.080 --> 00:30:39.280 align:middle line:90%
corporations.

00:30:39.280 --> 00:30:41.080 align:middle line:84%
And the way they
got away with that

00:30:41.080 --> 00:30:43.090 align:middle line:84%
was that they were
able to donate

00:30:43.090 --> 00:30:48.712 align:middle line:84%
a certain portion of the mining
materials and the raw materials

00:30:48.712 --> 00:30:53.440 align:middle line:84%
that they produced towards
the planetary regrowth,

00:30:53.440 --> 00:30:55.300 align:middle line:90%
towards the regrouping.

00:30:55.300 --> 00:31:00.670 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: Did these
corporations sell the things

00:31:00.670 --> 00:31:05.030 align:middle line:84%
that they produced to
the people of the planet?

00:31:05.030 --> 00:31:06.880 align:middle line:90%
>>RICE: No.

00:31:06.880 --> 00:31:09.460 align:middle line:90%
They sold them elsewhere.

00:31:09.460 --> 00:31:14.260 align:middle line:84%
They donated a portion of
their mining or their resource

00:31:14.260 --> 00:31:16.870 align:middle line:84%
production or whatever it
was that they were doing--

00:31:16.870 --> 00:31:19.930 align:middle line:84%
because it wasn't just
for mining of minerals--

00:31:19.930 --> 00:31:22.990 align:middle line:90%


00:31:22.990 --> 00:31:26.260 align:middle line:84%
they donated a certain
portion of that as a payment.

00:31:26.260 --> 00:31:28.570 align:middle line:84%
And I imagine that a
large percentage of that

00:31:28.570 --> 00:31:31.510 align:middle line:90%
went to the 13 families.

00:31:31.510 --> 00:31:35.590 align:middle line:84%
And then the rest of it was
taken off planet for sale

00:31:35.590 --> 00:31:36.490 align:middle line:90%
elsewhere.

00:31:36.490 --> 00:31:38.980 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: Would it be fair
to say that the whole idea

00:31:38.980 --> 00:31:44.630 align:middle line:84%
of corporate culture could be
a result of Draco interference?

00:31:44.630 --> 00:31:47.170 align:middle line:84%
>>RICE: Well based on the
information that I had

00:31:47.170 --> 00:31:50.800 align:middle line:84%
and the complete infiltration
by the Mars Germans into every

00:31:50.800 --> 00:31:54.070 align:middle line:84%
major corporation on the planet
from one end of the spectrum

00:31:54.070 --> 00:31:58.540 align:middle line:84%
to the other-- aerospace to
agriculture to petrochem to gas

00:31:58.540 --> 00:32:00.520 align:middle line:90%
to oil--

00:32:00.520 --> 00:32:05.410 align:middle line:84%
they were already infiltrated
by the Mars Germans.

00:32:05.410 --> 00:32:07.900 align:middle line:84%
Now the Mars Germans,
as we've discussed,

00:32:07.900 --> 00:32:11.340 align:middle line:84%
are, in a certain respect,
proxies of the Draco.

00:32:11.340 --> 00:32:16.210 align:middle line:84%
And so the Draco controlling
those proxies so that they

00:32:16.210 --> 00:32:17.740 align:middle line:90%
can further their efforts.

00:32:17.740 --> 00:32:22.570 align:middle line:84%
Who's to say that those
mining and the resources that

00:32:22.570 --> 00:32:26.680 align:middle line:84%
were taken weren't
used by the Draco

00:32:26.680 --> 00:32:28.900 align:middle line:84%
to help create some of
the other hybrids that

00:32:28.900 --> 00:32:30.040 align:middle line:90%
were used elsewhere?

00:32:30.040 --> 00:32:32.680 align:middle line:84%
Who's to say that
they weren't using

00:32:32.680 --> 00:32:36.940 align:middle line:84%
those materials for
producing or building

00:32:36.940 --> 00:32:39.910 align:middle line:90%
new ships or new facilities?

00:32:39.910 --> 00:32:40.780 align:middle line:90%
>>JAY: Or spiders.

00:32:40.780 --> 00:32:43.125 align:middle line:90%
>>RICE: Or spiders, exactly.

00:32:43.125 --> 00:32:45.640 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: And we really wouldn't
know, because the corporation

00:32:45.640 --> 00:32:48.640 align:middle line:84%
is an entity unto itself,
what they're really doing.

00:32:48.640 --> 00:32:49.900 align:middle line:90%
>>RICE: That's right.

00:32:49.900 --> 00:32:51.400 align:middle line:84%
Especially if they're
off the planet

00:32:51.400 --> 00:32:54.350 align:middle line:84%
and out of the way of any
laws, rules, and regulations.

00:32:54.350 --> 00:32:57.280 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: And since the 13 families
are running the place, that's

00:32:57.280 --> 00:32:58.080 align:middle line:90%
going to be a norm.

00:32:58.080 --> 00:32:59.663 align:middle line:84%
>>RICE: That's going
to be their norm.

